eir inner regions, which leads\nto the mass-segregation effect. Our study indicates that NGC 5617 and Trumpler\n22 are dynamically relaxed but the other pair of clusters are not. Orbital\nalongwith the physical parameters show that the clusters in both pairs are\nphysically connected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2021 08:30:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-17"}
