arcmin in radius around the center of NGC 6624. This has allowed us to localize\nmany of the pulsars in the cluster, demonstrating the beamforming capabilities\nof the TRAPUM software backend and paving the way for the upcoming MeerKAT\nglobular cluster pulsar survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Mar 2021 14:50:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-24"}
